# Task

Export all new types from core/mod.rs and lib.rs.

## Files to Modify

### crates/dspy-rs/src/core/mod.rs
```rust
// Add modules
mod call_result;
mod errors;
// signature.rs already exists

// Add exports
pub use call_result::{CallResult, FieldMeta, ConstraintResult};
pub use errors::{PredictError, ParseError, ConversionError, LmError, JsonishError};
pub use signature::{Signature, FieldSpec, ConstraintSpec, ConstraintKind};
// Keep MetaSignature export for backward compatibility
```

### crates/dspy-rs/src/lib.rs
```rust
// Add to existing pub use core::...
pub use core::{
    // Existing
    MetaSignature, Module, Optimizable,
    // New typed API
    Signature, FieldSpec, ConstraintSpec, ConstraintKind,
    CallResult, FieldMeta, ConstraintResult,
    PredictError, ParseError, ConversionError, LmError,
};
```

## Verification

```rust
// Should all work:
use dspy_rs::{Signature, PredictError, CallResult};
use dspy_rs::core::{FieldSpec, ConstraintKind};
```

## Search Context
- Use morph: `pub use` in crates/dspy-rs/src/core/mod.rs for existing pattern
- Use morph: `pub use core::` in crates/dspy-rs/src/lib.rs
